.DT
check_dir
$MUDNAME$ Creator Help
check_dir

.SH Name
.SP 5 5
check_dir -  This method attempts to load in the save file information for the specified directory.
.EP

.SH Syntax
.SI 5
void check_dir(string dir)
.EI

.SH Parameters
.SI 5
%^BOLD%^dir%^RESET%^ - the directory to load the save information for
.EI

.SH Defined in
.SI 5
/handlers/map_helper.c
.EI

.SH Description
.SP 5 5

This method attempts to load in the save file information for
the specified directory.  If the directory has no save file
then the mappings will all be initialised to empty.  It will cause
the previous directory to be saved if this is attempting to load a
different one.
.EP

.SH See also
.SP 5 5
save_dir()

.EP

